# vkcube

> Test Vulkan rendering.
> See also: `glxgears`.
> More information: <https://github.com/krh/vkcube>.

- Run a Vulkan test window:

`vkcube`

- Use a specific display protocol:

`vkcube --wsi {{xlib|wayland|...}}`

- Display help:

`vkcube -h`
